From 80bc8ee8e4b8236e909349e1f436ae4d0aab5ea1 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Christopher Sellers <1@christophersellers.com>
Date: Mon, 9 Mar 2026 15:07:17 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] feat: wire supplier dashboard + trace page to real admin
 service API

Replace hardcoded mock data in supplier dashboard and trace page with
live API calls to the admin service's supplier endpoints.

Backend:
- Add GET /v1/supplier/facilities endpoint to list all supplier facilities

Frontend:
- Supplier dashboard: fetches real facilities, compliance scores, gaps,
  and TLCs via apiClient; supports create facility and FDA export
- Trace page: queries CTE events by TLC code via FDA export preview
  endpoint, derives supply chain path from event sequence
- api-client: add listSupplierFacilities(), extend FDA preview with
  tlc_code filter param

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
